    Vaginal microbiome data from "Replication and refinement of a vaginal microbial signature of preterm birth in two racially distinct cohorts of US women" by Calahan et al., 2017, PNAS.

    vm_data.Rd

    A dataset containing the 16S rRNA sequencing counts from longitudinal samples of pregnant subjects throughout their pregnancy.

    vm_data

    Format

    A list of three data frames

    counts

    The number of times a given ASV (columns) was sequenced in a given sample (rows) material.

    sample_info

    Information about each sample including sequencing info (e.g. primers) and information about subjects and individual samples such as collection time.

    taxonomy

    Taxonomy table providing taxonomic information about each ASV.
